android.car.content.pm

类 CarAppBlockingPolicyService

  • java.lang.Object
    • Service
      • android.car.content.pm.CarAppBlockingPolicyService

  • public abstract class CarAppBlockingPolicyService
extends Service
    Service to be implemented by Service which wants to control app blocking policy. App should require android.car.permission.CONTROL_APP_BLOCKING to launch Service implementation. Additionally the APK should have the permission to be launched by Car Service. The implementing service should declare SERVICE_INTERFACE in its intent filter as action.
